ing makes it possible to spread join.me throughout the organization, without hidden fees or additional costs per minute. Plus, unlimited audio is included, so you never have to put a cap on your collaboration. Plus, unlimited audio is included, so you never have to put a cap on your collaboration.','Pricing','','publish','closed','closed','','pricing','','','2015-11-06 07:46:05','2015-11-06 07:46:05','',0,'http://localhost:8080/?page_id=9',3,'page','',0),(10,1,'2015-11-03 08:09:30','2015-11-03 08:09:30','','Pricing','','inherit','closed','closed','','9-revision-v1','','','2015-11-03 08:09:30','2015-11-03 08:09:30','',9,'http://localhost:8080/index.php/9-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(11,1,'2015-11-03 08:09:42','2015-11-03 08:09:42','','Blog','','publish','closed','closed','','blog','','','2015-11-03 08:11:20','2015-11-03 08:11:20','',0,'http://localhost:8080/?page_id=11',4,'page','',0),(12,1,'2015-11-03 08:09:42','2015-11-03 08:09:42','','Blog','','inherit','closed','closed','','11-revision-v1','','','2015-11-03 08:09:42','2015-11-03 08:09:42','',11,'http://localhost:8080/index.php/11-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(13,1,'2015-11-03 08:12:12','2015-11-03 08:12:12','Simple per-user pricing makes it possible to spread join.me throughout the organization, without hidden fees or additional costs per minute. Plus, unlimited audio is included, so you never have to put a cap on your collaboration. Simple per-user pricing makes it possible to spread join.me throughout the organization, without hidden fees or additional costs per minute. Plus, unlimited audio is included, so you never have to put a cap on your collaboration. Plus, unlimited audio is included, so you never have to put a cap on your collaboration.','About Us','','publish','closed','closed','','about-us','','','2015-11-19 10:15:19','2015-11-19 10:15:19','',0,'http://localhost:8080/?page_id=13',5,'page','',0),(14,1,'2015-11-03 08:12:12','2015-11-03 08:12:12','','About us','','inherit','closed','closed','','